p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black">讲者：</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black">秦波博士，副教授；</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black"><img src="https://edu-image.nosdn.127.net/4D5B6DBD8664FD627161245E9484440F.JPG?imageView&amp;thumbnail=520x520&amp;quality=100" id="1" style="width: 103px; height: 123px;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black"><br></span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;background: white"><span style="font-size:15px;font-family:Wingdings;color:black">l<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: \'Times New Roman\'">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black">开源数据库系统</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black">讲者：</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black">张孝博士，教授；</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: black"><img src="https://edu-image.nosdn.127.net/12B071935A5AF8E981A8A75A798BD3D4.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=520x520&amp;quality=100" id="1" style="width: 108px; height: 138px;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 56px;text-indent: 0;background: white"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: 新宋体;color: b