Microsoft Yahei&quot;, verdana; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, verdana; line-height: 19.6px;">总评成绩达到60分但未达到80分者，本课程成绩为合格。</span></span></p>\n<p style="outline: none; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, verdana; line-height: 19.6px;"><br></span></span></p>\n<p style="outline: none; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, verdana; line-height: 19.6px;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">现已取消免费证书，所有证书均付费。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;"><br></span></span><br></p>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style="font-family: sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, verdana; line-height: 19.6px;"><br></span></p>\n<p><br></p>', '<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;">*数据库系统概论（基础篇）2019年2月19日开课</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">*数据库系统概论（高级篇）2019年3月5日开课</span></p>', '<p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第1讲 数据库新技术概述</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">数据库技术50年发展回顾与启示</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">新技术篇简介</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 1