	(1206423806, '培养学术交流、求职、海外留学与商务场景下进行英文演讲与演示所必备的知识与技能，同时塑造全球化视角、跨文化思维，提升跨文化沟通技巧，融合教师个人丰富经验。', '<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif, Helvetica; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 如果你希望在求职中用英文进行流利的面试，在申请出国留学时能够打动面试官，在非常正式的学术交流或专业演示中有良好表现，那么你需要的不是一门普通的英语课，而是在这些领域有过丰富阅历的教师愿意毫无保留地从语言到思维做全方面的知识与经验传授。本课程从教师2002年在法国巴黎高商用十分钟英文演讲赢得MBA学生会主席的经历说起，从快速的语音校正和美式语调开始，优先传授跨文化思维的塑造，然后才从语言与非语言技巧、积极词汇量建设加工你的语言基础，重点强调自我介绍和英文面试两大应用场景，并请美国专家专门从母语者角度对中国学习者提出提纲挈领的建议，最后引导大家共同进行持续学习的策略。</span></p>', NULL, '2020-03-01', '2020-06-30', '<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">完成课程相关任务，获得相应分数。总分100分，60分及格，85分及以上优秀。课程提供合格证书和优秀证书，证书申请需付费。取消免费证书。</p>\n<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: disc;">\n <li><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">单元测验（5道单选）成绩占比36%，共计36分</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">第三周 单元测验&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;9&nbsp;</span>points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">第四周 单元测验&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>9 points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">第五周 单元测验&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;9&nbsp;</span>points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">第六章 单元测验&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;9</span>&nbsp;points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><br></p>\n<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: disc;">\n <li><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">作业成绩及同伴互评表现占比60%，共计60分</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">Homework No. 1: Voice Recording 20 points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">Homework No. 2: Giving a Speech 20 points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">Homework No. 3: Giving a Speech 20 points</p>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><br></p>\n<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: disc;">\n <li><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">课程活跃度占比4%，共计4分</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">在“课堂交流区”中回复主帖4次以上 4 points</p>\n<p>注意：</p>\n<p>1. 是课堂交流区，不是课堂讨论区；</p>\n<p>2.课堂交流区内学生不能发帖；</p>\n<p>3.课堂交流区内评论不计分；</p>\n<p>4. 匿名回复也不计分。</p>\n<p><br></p>', NULL, '<p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第一章 学习策略 Learning Strategy</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.1 谁该学这门课</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.6 英语演讲与演示的学习方法与课程流程</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.2 讲师自我介绍与课程范围</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.4 说好英语内在环境胜过外在环境</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK1 - 专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.5 英语演讲并不困难</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">1.3 精通英语的四个要素</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK1 - 补全思维导图</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第二章 语音语调 Pronunciation and intonation</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK2 -专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.9 美语语调的培养 Putting on American Accent</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.7 英音和美音的转换关键 Switching Between British Accent and American Accent</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.3 体会各国英语发音之间的差异 Appreciate different Englishes</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.4 英语音标中的元音 Vowels</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.6 常错音的纠正 Frequently mispronounced</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.2 中国学生英语口语的主要问题 Major issues in pronunciation</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.8 快速复习与单音发音作业1 Quick Review and Homework No.1</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.5 英语音标中的辅音 Consonants</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">2.1 英语要比汉语好学得多 English easier than Chinese</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">作业一 > Homework No.1 : Voice Recording</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">作业: Homework No. 1: Voice Recording</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第三章 中西文化差异与全球化视角Cultural Differences and Global Perspective</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.7 全球化视角下英语演讲的4个建议 (3) Four suggestions for making speak with global perspective</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">演讲作业 Homework No.2 Giving a Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.1 竞选巴黎高商学生会主席的演讲 Personal story: The speech that won presidency</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.5 全球化视角下英语演讲的4个建议 (1) Four suggestions for making speak with global perspective</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK3 - 专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.2 案例演讲分析与总结 Case analysis and lessons drawn</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.8 演讲作业 Homework No.2</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.3 中西文化的差异 Cultural differences between China and western world</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK3 - 补全思维导图</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.4 个人故事"I only kiss the one I love" Personal story: “I only kiss the one I love”</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">3.6 全球化视角下英语演讲的4个建议 (2) Four suggestions for making speak with global perspective</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">第三周 单元测验</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【第三周】 单元测验</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【作业二】演讲作业 Homework No.2 Giving a Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第四章 演讲中的语言技能与非语言技Verbal and non-verbal skills</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK4 - 专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.7 演讲开头的方式 How to Start a Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.3 身体移动与站姿 Body movement and Posture</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.2 TONE在演说中的重要性 Importance of Tone</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.5 视觉接触 Eye Contact</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.9 演讲结尾的方式 How to Conclude a Speech1</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.8 演讲中的路标词汇 Signposts in Your Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK4 - 补全思维导图</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.6 课后学习作业 After-class Learning Advice</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.1 肢体语言概述 Non-verbal Language</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">4.4 手势 Gesture</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">第四周 单元测验</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【第四周】单元测试</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第五章 积极词汇建设与图表描述Active vocabulary building</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.1 积极词汇量建设之避免性别歧视 Active vocabulary building</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.3 常用图表的相关英文表达 How data is used in Speeches and Presentations</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.2 积极词汇量建设之使语言适度 Being Approperiate-1 Describing Frequency</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.6 学习范例1：Khan如何使用图表 How did Khan use charts</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK5 - 补全思维导图</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.8 两个数据描述练习 Practice -describe the graph</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.11 下讲预告 Forecast</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.9 各类英语考试对词汇的要求 Active vocabulary building</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.4 练习描述数据变化 Describing changes in data</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.5 练习描述数据变化 Describing changes in data</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.10 为演讲如何建设积极词汇量 How to Active vocabulary</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK5 -专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">5.7 学习范例2：Hans的倾情数据使用 portrait of use data</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">第五周 单元测验</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【第五周】单元测验</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第六章 面试和自我介绍 Interviews & Self Introduction</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.7 要点四：自我介绍 Self-introduction</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK6 - 专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.8 作业练习 Homework</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.3 面试官看重的一些要素 Elements of the interviewer valued</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">作业练习 Homework No. 3: Giving a Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.5 要点二：面试中的礼节 Interview etiquette</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.4 要点一：面试前的准备 Prepare before the interview</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.1 英语在面试中的重要性及做为面试官的经历 The importance of English in the interview and As the interviewer\'s experience</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.6 要点三：面试中的策略 Interview Strategies</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">6.2 面试中的四个重要部分 Four important part of the interview</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">第六章 单元测试</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【第六章】单元测试</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">【作业三】Homework No. 3: Giving a Speech</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#333333"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第七章 看看外教怎么说 Native expert’s view</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">7.9 要注意的文化差异</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">7.7 演讲中的其他要素与演讲的准备与练习</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">WEEK7 - 专题讨论</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">7.4 怎样做一个好的演讲</span></span></p><p><span style="color:#999999"><span style="font-size: 13px;">7.6 演讲中的障碍与