-size:12px;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-weight:normal">切勿将本课程的测验题及答案在互联网上发布。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=";margin-bottom:0;line-height:15px;background:white;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;outline: none;white-space:pre-wrap;word-spacing:0px"><strong><span style="word-wrap: break-word"><span style="word-wrap: break-word"><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="word-wrap: break-word"><strong><span style="font-size:12px;font-family: 宋体;color:black;font-weight:normal">声明</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=";margin-bottom:0;line-height:15px;background:white;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;outline: none;white-space:pre-wrap;word-spacing:0px"><strong><span style="word-wrap: break-word"><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-weight:normal">本课程部分图片、视频来自网络及其他公开出版物，为教学需要在此借鉴。在此对所引用资料的作者及出版发布单位表示感谢！</span></strong></p>\n<p style=";margin-bottom:0;line-height:15px;background:white;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;outline: none;white-space:pre-wrap;word-spacing:0px"><strong><span style="word-wrap: break-word"><span style="font-size:12px;color:black;font-weight:normal">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=